---
title: Garden Veggie Soup with Homemade Noodles Supercharge your skills with this advanced recipe!
description: With just a few ingredients and a little kneading, you can make easy homemade egg noodle dough. Now comes the fun part: You’ll snip it with kitchen shears right into a hearty pot of garden veggie soup that’s packed with carrot, onion, and herbaceous dill! With a final dollop of luscious crème fraîche, this impressive homemade noodle soup will warm you to the core (and win the hearts of anyone at your table).
